Tious here. I'm kind of surprised that this question came up, especialy on something that's over a year ago in age but sure, I can answer with my thought process easy enough.

Stress affects this kind of thing as well anon. Someone tense beyond belief, someone who is emotionally overcharged, especially after the embarassing tackle yesterday, the thinking she was being abandoned in the morning, the emotional connection in the couch, ending with her in the bed, now being loved by someone who clearly wants it as well? That can be a real rush of adrenaline and emotions, something overwhelming to someone who, while perhaps not a virgin, has cleary not been riding the cock carrousell like a professional e621 character would have. Clamping down hard as she got more nervous in the heat of the moment (especially as she has a more athletic background) seemed very much logical to me as something which could be interperted as both ways of physically blocking and a much, much less filthy and realistic way of doing the whole first timer thing.

First times often suck anon. The clear lack of experience, the blood, the wrong expectations of what both side knows and doesn't know, the wrong expectations of stamina and more, the potential awkwardness of the act itself, so on. I decided to sidestep that into a more clean, idealised kind of event, something enjoyable to read, and with this element of plausible ambiguity in case anyone wishes to think her a non virgin. She's not portrayed to be the most experienced one that ever hit the field, but reasonable enough to place her as a non virgin in case you would like her to be one. I myself like her more as one, but hey, who am I to stop my readers from forming their own dream worlds with their own variations of the enviorements and characters?
